doctype html
html(lang="en")
  include bloghead.pug
  body
    include blogheader.pug

    //- Main Blog Post Section
    .container.mt-5
        .row
            .main-blog-post.col-md-12.text-center
                .position-relative
                    img.img-fluid(src="images/images11.avif", alt="Mom and Daughter cooking", data-author-name="Maria", data-author-interests="Cooking", data-author-image-url="images/photo-1556040220-4096d522378d.avif")
                    //- Button positioned in the middle of the image
                    button.btn.btn-warning.position-absolute.top-50.start-50.translate-middle Click Image

    //- Smaller Blog Posts Section
    .container.mt-5
        .row
            .col-md-4
                article.blog-post
                    .position-relative
                        img.img-fluid(src="images/photo-1712221370157-922ea45f0605.avif", alt="Post Image 1", data-author-name="Jordan", data-author-interests="Travel", data-author-image-url="images/imagesp9.avif")
                        button.btn.btn-warning.position-absolute.top-50.start-50.translate-middle Click Image
                    h3 Vacation 2024
                    p Our journey to this small village in Italy was a testament to the timeless allure of the Italian countryside and the enduring spirit of its people. As we bid arrivederci to the village and its warm embrace, we carried with us cherished memories and a newfound appreciation for the magic of Italyâ€”a land where every moment is a celebration of life, love, and la dolce vita.
                    p Tuesday, April 11, 2024 | 10:05 AM
            .col-md-4
                article.blog-post
                    .position-relative
                        img.img-fluid(src="images/image4.avif", alt="Post Image 2", data-author-name="Amber", data-author-interests="Fashion", data-author-image-url="images/premium_photo-1665663927708-e3287b105c44.avif")
                        button.btn.btn-warning.position-absolute.top-50.start-50.translate-middle Click Image
                    h3 Comfort in my sneakers
                    p In a world where comfort is king, comfortable sneakers reign supreme. From their supportive designs to their stylish aesthetics, these sneakers are the ultimate footwear choice for anyone who values both style and comfort. So go ahead, lace up a pair of comfortable sneakers and step into a world of endless possibilities, where every step is a journey worth taking.
                    p Tuesday, April 11, 2024 | 1:39 PM
            .col-md-4
                article.blog-post
                    .position-relative
                        img.img-fluid(src="images/imagesp10.avif", alt="Post Image 3", data-author-name="Cody", data-author-interests="Cars", data-author-image-url="photo-1626516912440-9ad2fa422978.avif")
                        button.btn.btn-warning.position-absolute.top-50.start-50.translate-middle Click Image
                    h3 New Ride
                    p Step into the world of automotive elegance as we unveil the sheer beauty and sophistication of my brand new white car. From its sleek silhouette to its cutting-edge features, this vehicle is a testament to style, innovation, and pure driving pleasure.
                    p Friday, April 15, 2024 | 12:10 PM

    // Blog Submission Form
    #blogFormContainer.container.mt-5(style="display: none;")
      form(action="/submit-blog", method="post")
        .form-group
          label(for="blogContent") Blog Content:
          textarea#blogContent.form-control(rows="10", name="blogContent")
        button.btn.btn-warning(type="submit") Submit New Blog

    include blogfooter.pug
    include blogscripts.pug
    // Include modal here
    include blogsubmodal.pug
    script(src="js/blogscripts.js")
    
    